Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六话 以上智为问者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策还有孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想来邀请吕蒙小姐和吕布小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和伯符姐姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有看到吕布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小布怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以读出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天以来 我拥有了好多美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 以前的我又有着怎么样的回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到这里 我就会坐立难安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要去寻找我的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个勾玉...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得小布会去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不担心小布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她自己决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们担心也是无济于事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就不要再说吕布的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什么都问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底去哪里了 吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙...孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了 听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙刚刚说了「你到底去哪里了 吕布」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在外面偷听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是在担心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙也很担心小布吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不去就是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了去就要去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙竟然攻击人关节 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗士的证明...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是被人找麻烦 就是因为这个勾玉的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 斗士到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有记忆...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也什么都不知道 除了自己的名字以外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是来找我麻烦的人告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏侯惇元让 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙真的生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还被赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小布也是 要是写下去处就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前公瑾哥哥有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个制服是洛阳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的吕布小姐而言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够成为找回过去的线索的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有那件制服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个 仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛阳在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛阳高校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以问你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对孟德这个名字有印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟德...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛阳的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的死党
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己的名字都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还记得他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我很重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有重要的人吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去问问公瑾哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙果然好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的你 有点太粘人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 洛阳...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当家的董卓仲颖死后 渐渐失去了管制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该已经废校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的曾经在这里上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你都是斗士的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的过去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许也有我过去的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们自己来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会冒着被小蒙盘问的麻烦露面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和她一起的那个男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他交给夏侯渊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的曾经在这里上过学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是有着我的回忆的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案由我来告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你用这么生疏的称呼对待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受挫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的习惯到你会兴奋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我也应该很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这种类型啊 好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有...勾玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是斗士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你女朋友这话 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你以前的熟识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以问她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的熟识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯惇元让
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重归...许昌学院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许昌学院？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是女朋友 是说现在已经不了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是为了某个目的才接近我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我看穿了 将计就计的也反过来利用你罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们彼此也都乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像把一切都忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样更方便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那个家伙还存在于我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙没有告诉过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她变成真正的女人是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯渊妙才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯惇 和我一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得你们什么都知道似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独眼小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听夏侯渊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到许昌 来协助我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想见他吧 曹操孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚说了什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你带回...许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不就说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很看不惯你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 这样就完全清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用兵器对付手无寸铁的人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用刀子对付手无寸铁的人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 小惇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伯符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常和你一起打斗 一起做傻事的伯符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻事...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在勾玉上面写了名字 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不许叫我笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策...伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是孙策伯符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当...当然是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么严肃...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有一件事我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你是笨蛋这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你叫了我笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯独非常不愿意被小惇叫笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和你断绝朋友关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想起了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙 仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布小姐也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好多事情要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惇 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把制服弄坏了 又要被妈妈骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就交给我 小惇你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能忍受总是被女生救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被那个家伙带到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了寻找以前的记忆来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从...于我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别总是让我重复
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个装模作样的家伙说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见孟德的话 就要协助他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在寻找的死党孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让你们把他作为交易的筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惇 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你很重要的修理工具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球的话是球场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道的话是柔道场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么格斗的话是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜...猜谜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不行 因为我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条街就是我们的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把圣地弄得一团糟 就想回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗中 最重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯渊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要和那个装模作样的家伙合伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果孟德在许昌等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以我自己的方式去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 出了一肚子的怨气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要像这样 在裂开的地方涂上油灰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有用锉子慢慢地涂平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惇还是和以前一样的笨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙 小布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惇 你要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的答案一定都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙子曰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝气锐 昼气惰 暮气归
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在早上最精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午开始涣散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚开始寻求休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起来品尝便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去见妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小惇是妈妈的男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 弄乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 又有谁在背后议论我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是美发沙龙的那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前新开的那个药房的店长也是个很有型的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小布好像比以前开朗了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谈论我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的妈妈在交往的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常恩爱的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的肚子里有了小惇的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子里有了我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承认 我绝对不会承认的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯惇大人请您冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙子曰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承担责任是男人的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 孙子曰...没有说过这种话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七话 始若处女
